{code}

The crash occurs on both 2.7.1 and 2.7.2-RC1.

The same code in the interpreter reports an error instead of crashing:

{code}
scala> class A(a: Foo[_]#BAR)
<console>:1: error: unbound wildcard type
       class A(a: Foo[_]#BAR)
{code}

